<h3>Set a Baseline Before Every Refresh</h3>
<p>Before you change anything, record:
- Current organic traffic (last 30 days)
- Current average position for the target keyword
- Current CTR
- Current number of ranking keywords</p>
<p>Without a baseline, you cannot measure improvement.</p>
